4️⃣ Add Retry (Production Pattern)
public void safeTransfer(Long fromId, Long toId, Double amount) {

    int retries = 3;

    while (retries > 0) {
        try {
            transferWithNewTx(fromId, toId, amount);
            return;
        } catch (ObjectOptimisticLockingFailureException ex) {
            retries--;
            try { Thread.sleep(200); } catch (InterruptedException ignored) {}
        }
    }

    throw new RuntimeException("Transfer failed after retries");
}

5️⃣ Important — Use NEW Transaction for Retry
